{"tid":1032030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公廁洗手感染食肉菌　曾來港美女特技演員　臉長血瘡留8厘米疤痕","createTime":"2019-02-22T05:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T02:22:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"79a20975aa57dceb1c5102f3938283e4d6f1a0af","tid":1032030,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T05:33:38.000Z","msg":"上完廁所要洗手是常識吧！相信不少人都會認為洗手液有抗菌功能，所以裝著洗手液的容器應是乾淨的，但美國一名女子卻因為使用公廁的洗手液，意外感染到食肉菌，導致毀容且幾乎喪命。<br />\n威瑟斯（Rachel Star Withers）是美國荷里活特技女演員，曾到過香港分享自己克服精神分裂症的經歷。她憶述，從小就能看到別人看不見的「大眼怪物」，童年在驚恐中度過。<br />\n跨過一個難關，生命又給威瑟斯另一個難關。<br />\n<br />\n暗瘡般小傷口不斷擴大​<br />\n當日威瑟斯在公廁用過洗手液，其後皮膚出現異樣，胸口反覆泛起紅疹，臉上浮現一些像暗瘡般的小傷口。隨着病情惡化，她臉上的紅點不斷擴大，越來越深，附近皮膚皺成一團，灰白乾枯如喪屍般。<br />\n令人心驚的「食肉菌」其實沒有特定某一種細菌，食肉菌感染是指由不同細菌引發的壞死性筋膜炎，除甲類鏈球菌外，常見於海水的弧菌以至大腸桿菌均可能導致有關症狀。威瑟斯感染的是名為產酸克雷伯氏菌（Klebsiella oxytoca）的大腸桿菌，一般存在於人體腸道且無害，但如果免疫力較弱的人受感染，可引起腹痛、肺炎及尿道炎等，甚至致命。<br />\n<br />\n大難不死 醫生形容她好運<br />\n威瑟斯感染了食肉菌後多次求醫但未獲正視，過了一段長時間才得到正確診斷，在治療過程中，惡菌與受感染的皮膚組織「同歸於盡」，在她臉上留下了約7.5厘米的疤痕和大大小小的坑洞。然而，醫生還是覺得威瑟斯很幸運，因為按照食肉菌感染的致命率和她患病之久，她應該早已不在人世。<br />\n清潔專家普羅達諾娃（Ralitsa Prodanova）指出，許多人誤以為皂液器會「自我消毒」，實情卻是除非清潔工在重裝洗手液時徹底清洗容器，否則將成為細菌滋生的溫床，即使裝的是抗菌洗手液也不例外。她建議外出時攜帶個人洗手液，以避免細菌感染。<br />\n澳洲斯威本科技大學化學教授帕隆博（Enzo Palombo）稱，兒童、長者、孕婦和免疫系統有問題人士感染食肉菌的風險最高，應該特別謹慎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2469887/org/5960352a017615af492b686afd07d5a6.JPG/nBhk_i3cvT3_ElKzecwELtGdzuB9RUIcUBvNhVAbzYU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2469887%2Forg%2F5960352a017615af492b686afd07d5a6.JPG%2FnBhk_i3cvT3_ElKzecwELtGdzuB9RUIcUBvNhVAbzYU&h=36d21194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2469879/org/e9e4527123f43ba8e65a2d7383e7c293.jpg/IPouMt0ggrEyzklYOFtVz8S16-CJp-A0VhfToFYX06A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2469879%2Forg%2Fe9e4527123f43ba8e65a2d7383e7c293.jpg%2FIPouMt0ggrEyzklYOFtVz8S16-CJp-A0VhfToFYX06A&h=176ec2de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2469873/org/5c00f949225a148d685840b47095fda7.JPG/d-S8vjqAZr3PYlowEk_aFvClX5sJJdh-SHYMYEh2DGA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2469873%2Forg%2F5c00f949225a148d685840b47095fda7.JPG%2Fd-S8vjqAZr3PYlowEk_aFvClX5sJJdh-SHYMYEh2DGA&h=62f31550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2469880/org/203b872229cad27eed3643b175adad40.JPG/Cl9IxP8HwMGAyo6nlGsow_fUyPaTe-MI5vjrB-b46wc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2469880%2Forg%2F203b872229cad27eed3643b175adad40.JPG%2FCl9IxP8HwMGAyo6nlGsow_fUyPaTe-MI5vjrB-b46wc&h=bf99baf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2469889/org/4deccc4283c87060ad77ed33c53dc009.JPG/thNxoQlCvZPMJ99iNE7NxokHn2Pmgmd5S53t4Eud7eA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2469889%2Forg%2F4deccc4283c87060ad77ed33c53dc009.JPG%2FthNxoQlCvZPMJ99iNE7NxokHn2Pmgmd5S53t4Eud7eA&h=590cf42f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b8ba153e7fb1698fce9b042d30fac34cce9456c","tid":1032030,"uid":174551,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T05:37:29.000Z","msg":"呢啲就有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab8ea923831923985dc7bd945882fdbd7b684e3","tid":1032030,"uid":25676,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"曾來港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都可以做標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e91345abef28bb2c603071fcaf994170dcd6f7","tid":1032030,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"從來唔用"},{"pid":"f88787260976ee932cdff7e2a85764fda2ed5283","tid":1032030,"